yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;doo2.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (544.76 KB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-17 16:17&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;支持食屎狗繼續交租&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930085&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=157401795668289e2f71acf3_63985614"/><published>2025-05-17T16:17:43+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>b323f2679dc9343cbe3edacbd3072498</id><title>大摩料美通脹升溫 聯儲局今年不減息</title><updated>2025-05-17T18:46:43+08:00</updated><author><name>驚青猛男</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T18:46:43+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572446050"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572446050"&gt;大摩料美通脹升溫聯儲局今年不減息&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="572446050" original-img="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250517/photo/bkn-20250517172350326-0517_00842_001_01p.jpg?20250517172350" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250517/photo/bkn-20250517172350326-0517_00842_001_01p.jpg?20250517172350" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/4d2870/f/800x0/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250517/photo/bkn-20250517172350326-0517_00842_001_01p.jpg?20250517172350"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;大行摩根士丹利認為，美國總統特朗普的對等關稅政策轉變，可能使美國經濟免於陷入衰退，但現有關稅措施仍會導致美國經濟陷入低增長及高通脹，使聯儲局可能要到明年3月才開始減息。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;該行指中美兩國近日公布的互降關稅措施，貿易衝突風險降溫，亦令整體美國的有效關稅稅率由高峰期的26%降至13%。然而，此水平的關稅仍遠高於今年初的2%，足以令美國經濟陷入低增長及高通脹環境。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;大摩預計，關稅的影響可能會從5月開始在通脹數據中顯現，預計年底前年度通脹率將上升到3至3.5%區間，第二季國內生產總值增長可能僅為1.6%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;隨着通脹升溫，該行因而維持聯儲局今年不會減息的預測不變，並料最快明年3月當局才有可能進行減息。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250517/bkn-20250517172350326-0517_00842_001.html" target="_blank" uhash="1684d291300efb5be24f84e9e0590498"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250517/bkn-20250517172350326-0517_00842_001.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930189&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=157401795668289e2f71acf3_63985614"/><published>2025-05-17T18:46:43+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>d6410224b63429b7cb341abb9ca4f091</id><title>房屋署...是否出了問題？！</title><updated>2025-05-17T19:18:03+08:00</updated><author><name>jackyfree2</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T19:18:03+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572446396"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572446396"&gt;20,000...嘅1倍當然係40,000喇~&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;咁2倍...自由係60,000架喇！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;難度...20,000嘅1倍依然係20,000咩？&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;房屋署個表，是否出現咗《重大》問題呢？&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16231715" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572446396" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_ef7ec4b7dacb1a4a8f49jvtm0x2FKz39.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/ea4b57/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_ef7ec4b7dacb1a4a8f49jvtm0x2FKz39.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16231715_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16231715&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_20250517_132259_Gallery.j